title: The Batman Strikes!
description:
The Batman Strikes! is a comic book series based on the Emmy Award-winning The Batman animated television series produced by Warner Bros. Although the series borrows many elements from previous Batman storylines, it does not follow the continuity set by the comic books, the film series, nor that of the previous Batman: The Animated Series or its spin-offs. The character designs were provided by Jackie Chan Adventures artist Jeff Matsuda and was noticeably lighter in tone than the previous animated series, depicting Batman as more lighthearted with a dry, ironic wit.
